728707f-a.title: Richmond: Clinton Avenue - Fillmore Street
728707f-a.text:
Clinton Avenue, at the S.W. corner of Fillmore Street, showing the interior of the Unitarian Church of Staten Island, looking toward the chancel.
Fall, 1928
P. L. Sperr
